an-compares-todays-market-to-the-dot-com-bubble-2020-06-13%3Famp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.nasdaq.com%2Farticles%2Fwhy-mark-cuban-compares-todays-market-to-the-dot-com-bubble-2020-06-13%253Famp&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=4b5e7870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.nasdaq.com/articles/why-mark-cuban-compares-todays-market-to-the-dot-com-bubble-2020-06-13%3Famp</a>"},{"pid":"159d91462e5c5ecebbaf8cc9b9424f0a1c621c6d","tid":2379090,"uid":24306,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟本支那股同美股一樣<br />\n全部9升<br />\n遲早閪冧"},{"pid":"2b9c21a76ed82cc83526f3954f6d9880146e8e0d","tid":2379090,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"美股泡沬仲大，一樣照升"},{"pid":"1654926929a9516cfc5572d526b0df4a015a43ed","tid":2379090,"uid":239912,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"愈係泡沫愈要槓桿<br />\n咁先贏到大錢"},{"pid":"d70768ffcde80a5cb6d0f70c29d9ebaa17ec3254","tid":2379090,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"159d91462e5c5ecebbaf8cc9b9424f0a1c621c6d","tid":2379090,"uid":24306,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟本支那股同美股一樣<br />\n全部9升<br />\n遲早閪冧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"升多1萬點先講啦"},{"pid":"1d018c25d232944ca55687e322e5b39268d7109f","tid":2379090,"uid":24306,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b9c21a76ed82cc83526f3954f6d9880146e8e0d","tid":2379090,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"美股泡沬仲大，一樣照升"},"ci